item.title: Word Table Light
item.description:
Design & Fabrication

Designer: Studio Word (Seoul)
Process: Additive Manufacturing (3D Printed)
Material: Gantri Plant Polymer (Sustainable, heat-resistant)
Dimensions: 10"H x 7"W x 7"D

item.title: Redefining the Cockpit: Why Materiality Matters
item.description:
Have you ever noticed how a generic accessory can ruin the carefully curated aesthetic of a premium vehicle interior?

At Vancroft, we operate on a simple principle: Cohesion.
